                        <foliation/>
                        <collation/>
                        <condition>
                           <list>
                              <item>
                                 <p>Vellum, about 8 3/4 in. by 5 3/8, consisting of 46 leaves, many
                                    of which are much stained and torn, especially foll. 3 — 6, 9,
                                    10, 17 — 21, 35, and 46. The quires, signed with letters, were
                                    originally 13 in number, but several are now lost, and only
                                       <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܓ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="syr"
                                       >ܝـ</foreign>, and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܒ</foreign>, are
                                    complete. Leaves are wanting after <locus from="2">foll.
                                       2</locus>, <locus from="6">6</locus>, <locus from="8"
                                       >8</locus>, <locus from="18">18</locus>, <locus from="19"
                                       >19</locus>, <locus from="20">20</locus>, <locus from="21"
                                       >21</locus>, <locus from="33">33</locus>, and <locus
                                       from="45">45</locus>. Each page has from 22 to 28 lines.</p>
                              </item>
                           </list>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <p>Content pending</p>
                     </layoutDesc>
